common_issues.title: Pieces Core Services Fails to Open Due to WebSocket Error
common_issues.description: Multiple users reported a WebSocketException with a 404 HTTP status code when attempting to open Pieces Core Services. The connection to 'http://127.0.0.1:39300/user/last_checked_in/stream#' fails to upgrade to a websocket.  The Pieces OS version is unknown. Users are running macOS 15.6 (Build 24G5065c) on an Apple M2 processor. Further investigation is needed to determine the root cause and potential solutions.
